# Undercurrent Project Rules

## AI Models

**ChatGPT 5.1 is the current latest OpenAI model** (released November 12, 2025). This project uses ChatGPT 5.1 for:
- Text generation (idea generation, onboarding chat, prompt creation)
- Image generation (idea cover images)

Do NOT suggest older models like GPT-4, GPT-4o, or GPT-3.5 unless specifically asked. ChatGPT 5.1 exists and is what we're using.

## Tech Stack

- **Framework:** Next.js (App Router)
- **Styling:** Tailwind CSS 4.1
- **Components:** shadcn/ui
- **Database & Auth:** Supabase with email auth
- **Hosting:** Vercel
- **AI:** ChatGPT 5.1 (OpenAI)

## Code Style

- Use TypeScript for all code
- Follow the design system in `docs/design-system.md`
- Store AI prompts as markdown files in `/prompts` folder
- Use Supabase client for all database operations

## Project Structure

```
/app              - Next.js App Router pages and layouts
/components       - React components
/lib              - Utility functions, Supabase client, etc.
/prompts          - AI prompt templates (markdown files)
/docs             - Documentation (PRD, design system)
```

## Git Workflow

- Always work in feature branches prefixed with `andrew/`
- Only one migration file per branch
- Don't commit to main directly
